{
  "book": 20,
  "chapter": 28,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The wicked flee though no one pursues, but the righteous are as bold as a lion. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wicked flee though no one pursues, but the righteous are as bold as a lion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When a country is rebellious, it has many rulers, but a ruler with discernment and knowledge maintains order. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When a country is rebellious, it has many rulers, but a ruler with discernment and knowledge maintains order."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A ruler who oppresses the poor is like a driving rain that leaves no crops. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A ruler who oppresses the poor is like a driving rain that leaves no crops."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Those who forsake instruction praise the wicked, but those who heed it resist them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Those who forsake instruction praise the wicked, but those who heed it resist them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Evildoers do not understand what is right, but those who seek the Lord understand it fully. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Evildoers do not understand what is right, but those who seek the Lord understand it fully."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Better the poor whose walk is blameless than the rich whose ways are perverse. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Better the poor whose walk is blameless than the rich whose ways are perverse."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A discerning son heeds instruction, but a companion of gluttons disgraces his father. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A discerning son heeds instruction, but a companion of gluttons disgraces his father."
